{"title":"GCM","uid":"17123eb273eb28de4ba456a5c252cb7a","slug":"credential-manager","date":"2023-10-28T15:09:09.608Z","updated":"2025-06-13T10:02:46.942Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/credential-manager.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/28/28tyr5UZbIVm7wX.png","content":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/git-ecosystem/git-credential-manager/blob/main/docs/multiple-users.md\">git凭据管理(git-credential-manager)-多用户</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"帮助命令\"><a href=\"#帮助命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"帮助命令\"></a>帮助命令</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">credential-manager</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">--help</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># Description:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   Commands for interacting with the GitHub host provider</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># Usage:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   git-credential-manager github [command] [options]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># Options:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   --no-ui         Do not use graphical user interface prompts</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   -?, -h, --help  Show help and usage information</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># Commands:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   list              List all known GitHub accounts.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   login             Add a GitHub account.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\">#   logout &lt;account&gt;  Remove a GitHub account.</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"查看凭据列表\"><a href=\"#查看凭据列表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"查看凭据列表\"></a>查看凭据列表</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">git</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">credential-manager</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">github</span><span style=\"color: #EEFFFF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">list</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># kidwen</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #545454; font-style: italic\"># levy</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"删除用户凭据\"><a href=\"#删除用户凭据\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除用户凭据\"></a>删除用户凭据</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-darker\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: 